object.name: Batch Processes
object.simulatedExtractionQuery:
SELECT *
BATCH_PROCESS BATCH_PROCESS,
  BATCH_PROCESS_D BPD
WHERE
  BP.BATCH_PROCESS_GID = BPD.BATCH_PROCESS_GID
  AND BP.IS_ENABLED = 'Y'
ORDER BY
  BP.DOMAIN_NAME,
  BP.BATCH_PROCESS_XID,
  BPD.SEQUENCE_NO
